00:37:17.160 --> 00:37:18.400
Is he a lizard or something?

00:37:18.400 --> 00:37:19.800
I can't remember what he is.

00:37:19.800 --> 00:37:22.792
All right, has anyone struggled
with visualization before?

00:37:22.792 --> 00:37:24.250
People who have
tried it, or anyone

00:37:24.250 --> 00:37:26.360
here who thinks they
can't visualize?

00:37:26.360 --> 00:37:28.790
Because quite often
there are some people.

00:37:28.790 --> 00:37:35.320
OK, so if you could just
think back to something,

00:37:35.320 --> 00:37:38.430
a pleasant experience
from last weekend.

00:37:38.430 --> 00:37:40.680
If you didn't have a pleasant
experience last weekend,

00:37:40.680 --> 00:37:42.670
you can go back to the
weekend before then.

00:37:42.670 --> 00:37:45.310
Go back as far as you need to.

00:37:45.310 --> 00:37:46.970
Maybe it was with
friends, with family.

00:37:46.970 --> 00:37:51.110
Just remembering
a nice situation.

00:37:51.110 --> 00:37:52.880
Maybe you were outside
having a barbecue,

00:37:52.880 --> 00:37:54.171
or out for a walk or something.

00:38:00.620 --> 00:38:02.530
Everyone think of something?

00:38:02.530 --> 00:38:03.290
Yeah?

00:38:03.290 --> 00:38:04.780
OK, all right.

00:38:04.780 --> 00:38:06.700
It's that amount
of effort that's

00:38:06.700 --> 00:38:08.920
required for visualization.

00:38:08.920 --> 00:38:10.370
Just imagining something.

00:38:10.370 --> 00:38:14.290
In fact, imagination could be
another word for visualization.

00:38:14.290 --> 00:38:17.650
There's no kind of special,
extra thing that's needed.

00:38:17.650 --> 00:38:19.630
And often people struggle
with visualization,

00:38:19.630 --> 00:38:24.470
because there's a little bit too
much effort that goes into it.

00:38:24.470 --> 00:38:26.910
So I'd just like you to do
another thing for me now.

00:38:26.910 --> 00:38:28.610
So that's something
you've already done,

00:38:28.610 --> 00:38:30.430
so you might think,
yeah, well I'm

00:38:30.430 --> 00:38:33.190
remembering that rather
than imagining that.

00:38:33.190 --> 00:38:36.890
OK, so just imagine a good
friend of yours standing

00:38:36.890 --> 00:38:39.860
there in front of you.

00:38:39.860 --> 00:38:41.680
And just get in to
do, I don't know,

00:38:41.680 --> 00:38:44.650
jumping jacks or
something like that.

00:38:44.650 --> 00:38:47.120
Whenever, you ask them
to do anything they like.

00:38:47.120 --> 00:38:48.910
Just get them to do
some physical movement

00:38:48.910 --> 00:38:50.950
in front of you.

00:38:50.950 --> 00:38:52.810
Everyone imagine that.

00:38:52.810 --> 00:38:53.570
Yeah?

00:38:53.570 --> 00:38:54.150
OK.

00:38:54.150 --> 00:38:56.646
So again, it's something I'm
assuming it hasn't happened,

00:38:56.646 --> 00:38:58.020
maybe it did happen
last weekend.

00:38:58.020 --> 00:38:59.311
Maybe that's part of the thing.

00:38:59.311 --> 00:39:00.150
I don't know.

00:39:00.150 --> 00:39:02.260
But I'm assuming it
hasn't, and yet it's

00:39:02.260 --> 00:39:05.880
quite easy to turn
you mind towards that.

00:39:05.880 --> 00:39:09.130
Just that very kind
of gentle imagination

00:39:09.130 --> 00:39:12.890
is really all that's
required here.

00:39:12.890 --> 00:39:14.770
So again, I'm going to
lead you through it.

00:39:14.770 --> 00:39:17.490
These exercises, I know,
they're quite guided.

00:39:17.490 --> 00:39:20.290
There's quite a lot
commentary through it.

