00:39:40.310 --> 00:39:42.280
You're going to start
the exercise in exactly

00:39:42.280 --> 00:39:42.940
the same way.

00:39:42.940 --> 00:39:48.290
So still looking directly
ahead of yourself,

00:39:48.290 --> 00:39:52.890
not staring at any one
thing in particular.

00:39:52.890 --> 00:39:55.920
There's just that
very spacious sense,

00:39:55.920 --> 00:40:00.170
being able to see either
side, above and below.

00:40:04.750 --> 00:40:08.510
And when you're ready,
when you're comfortable,

00:40:08.510 --> 00:40:11.870
just taking those
deep breaths again.

00:40:11.870 --> 00:40:15.980
Breathing in through the nose,
and out through the mouth.

00:40:19.659 --> 00:40:21.950
We're a little bit easier
this time, as you breathe in,

00:40:21.950 --> 00:40:25.400
just a sense of the lungs
expanding as you breathe out,

00:40:25.400 --> 00:40:27.670
a sense of the body softening.

00:40:27.670 --> 00:40:28.840
Just two or three times.

00:40:31.710 --> 00:40:35.990
And then with the
exhalation, just

00:40:35.990 --> 00:40:38.020
gently closing the eyes again.

00:40:46.560 --> 00:40:51.930
OK, and still taking the
time just to ground the mind,

00:40:51.930 --> 00:40:54.960
be aware of the
physical sensations.

00:40:54.960 --> 00:40:57.570
The weight of the body
against the chair.

00:41:02.600 --> 00:41:05.728
Feet on the floor.

00:41:05.728 --> 00:41:11.072
Hands and arms on the legs.

00:41:23.130 --> 00:41:28.390
Starting to notice any sounds,
either inside or outside

00:41:28.390 --> 00:41:32.542
of the room,

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:48.130
And just bringing the
attention back to the body.

00:41:48.130 --> 00:41:49.950
Before we begin
the visualization,

00:41:49.950 --> 00:41:51.750
just scanning down
in the same way

00:41:51.750 --> 00:41:57.560
as you did before,
without any expectation,

00:41:57.560 --> 00:42:01.140
without trying to
change anything.

00:42:01.140 --> 00:42:03.970
Just scanning from the
head down to the toes.

00:42:52.460 --> 00:42:54.590
If the mind wanders
off, just gently

00:42:54.590 --> 00:42:56.680
bring it back again
as you carry on.

00:43:28.960 --> 00:43:31.900
And just as before,
just touching

00:43:31.900 --> 00:43:35.375
on the breath, just
taking 20, 30 seconds.

00:43:40.640 --> 00:43:42.640
Just to notice how the
breath feels in the body.

00:44:30.980 --> 00:44:35.670
I'd just like you to
imagine, for a moment,

00:44:35.670 --> 00:44:37.340
that directly above
your head there's

00:44:37.340 --> 00:44:46.220
a steady flow of warm sunlight,
streaming down into the body.

00:44:49.090 --> 00:44:51.310
And just the same way on
a very bright day, you

00:44:51.310 --> 00:44:54.270
can see the sun streaming
through the clouds

00:44:54.270 --> 00:44:55.540
or the trees.

00:44:55.540 --> 00:44:59.000
In just the same
way, streaming down,

00:44:59.000 --> 00:45:02.220
flowing down, into the body.

00:45:02.220 --> 00:45:08.110
And we're going to imagine as
though this sunlight slowly

00:45:08.110 --> 00:45:10.760
fills the body up.

00:45:10.760 --> 00:45:14.630
And just notice what
happens as you move along.

00:45:14.630 --> 00:45:16.400
So I'd like you to
imagine it, streaming

00:45:16.400 --> 00:45:20.270
down through the body, down
the left hand side of the body,

00:45:20.270 --> 00:45:22.180
down the left leg
and all the way

00:45:22.180 --> 00:45:25.340
down to the foot and the toes.

00:45:25.340 --> 00:45:28.940
So it's almost as though
we're filling up a vase.

00:45:28.940 --> 00:45:35.180
And you just watch as
the small toes fills up,

00:45:35.180 --> 00:45:41.324
and the next, and
the next, next.

00:45:41.324 --> 00:45:41.824
Big toe.

00:45:41.824 --> 00:45:47.610
And it continues to flow
down, now filling the foot.

00:45:47.610 --> 00:45:50.670
Just that very warm,
spacious quality.

00:45:53.180 --> 00:45:58.435
Now moving up past the ankle
into the lower half of the leg.

00:46:02.500 --> 00:46:10.030
You just feel any tension
melting away, dissolving,

00:46:10.030 --> 00:46:14.040
as it moves up past the knee
into the upper half of the leg.

00:46:18.580 --> 00:46:24.370
The gentle, steady stream
flowing down through the body.

00:46:24.370 --> 00:46:30.770
Now all the way up towards
the hip and the pelvic area.

00:46:30.770 --> 00:46:33.510
And before we continue,
just notice the difference

00:46:33.510 --> 00:46:36.810
in feeling between your left
and right leg right now.

00:46:41.020 --> 00:46:42.840
But it continues to stream down.

00:46:42.840 --> 00:46:47.670
This time we go down the right
side, down the right leg,

00:46:47.670 --> 00:46:49.980
into the right foot.

