Starting with the small
toe, just watching

00:46:55.140 --> 00:47:00.970
as each part of
the foot, each toe,

00:47:00.970 --> 00:47:03.065
replaced by this very
spacious quality.

00:47:07.650 --> 00:47:19.240
Filling up the foot,
past the ankle,

00:47:19.240 --> 00:47:20.710
the lower half of the leg.

00:47:26.840 --> 00:47:33.010
Just watching as it
continues to travel upwards,

00:47:33.010 --> 00:47:36.770
past the knee into the
upper half of the leg,

00:47:36.770 --> 00:47:39.240
and just feeling any
tension melting away.

00:47:46.420 --> 00:47:51.390
All the way up to the waist.

00:47:51.390 --> 00:47:53.730
In just the same way as
with the other exercise,

00:47:53.730 --> 00:47:56.360
if the mind wanders, let
it wander, no problem.

00:47:56.360 --> 00:47:59.200
But when you realize
it's wandered, just

00:47:59.200 --> 00:48:03.670
gently bring the focus back
again to this visualization,

00:48:03.670 --> 00:48:09.890
this sense, this feeling
of warmth, spaciousness.

00:48:09.890 --> 00:48:15.014
As you watch now as it
begins to fill upwards.

00:48:15.014 --> 00:48:23.460
The lower stomach, the lower
back, as though everything just

00:48:23.460 --> 00:48:25.640
starts to give
away a little bit.

00:48:30.750 --> 00:48:43.110
Upwards towards the diaphragm,
the middle of the back,

00:48:43.110 --> 00:48:46.720
and up towards the chest,
in between the shoulders.

00:48:50.300 --> 00:48:51.970
Remembering where
that's coming from,

00:48:51.970 --> 00:48:53.940
above the head,
still streaming down.

00:48:58.200 --> 00:48:59.330
Dissolving any discomfort.

00:49:02.220 --> 00:49:04.860
It moves now up towards
the neck and the throat.

00:49:15.710 --> 00:49:19.260
Now coming down from above the
head up through the jaw area.

00:49:22.640 --> 00:49:24.015
Just feeling
everything dissolve.

00:49:27.687 --> 00:49:41.830
Up past the nose, the eyes, all
the way to the top of the head.

00:49:41.830 --> 00:49:44.090
And even when you get
the top of the head,

00:49:44.090 --> 00:49:50.040
even though the body is now
completely full of sunlight,

00:49:50.040 --> 00:49:53.440
it still continues to flow.

00:49:53.440 --> 00:49:57.950
And it's as though it just gets
a little bit bigger, a bit more

00:49:57.950 --> 00:50:02.860
spacious, going beyond
the confines of the body

00:50:02.860 --> 00:50:04.477
into the space around you.

00:50:10.560 --> 00:50:12.790
You can either just
sit comfortably,

00:50:12.790 --> 00:50:16.910
just for a few more
seconds with that feeling.

00:50:16.910 --> 00:50:18.730
Or, if you find it
helpful, you can just

00:50:18.730 --> 00:50:22.910
imagine that continuing on
outwards in every direction,

00:50:22.910 --> 00:50:27.260
as far as the mind
can imagine it,

00:50:27.260 --> 00:50:30.457
and just everyone else
benefiting from that experience

00:50:30.457 --> 00:50:31.290
as it goes outwards.

00:51:01.060 --> 00:51:03.720
Now as with last time, nothing
really to do at this stage,

00:51:03.720 --> 00:51:09.270
just allowing the mind
to expand outwards,

00:51:09.270 --> 00:51:13.755
enjoying that sense of
warmth and spaciousness.

00:51:28.350 --> 00:51:33.490
And then just gently bringing
the attention back again,

00:51:33.490 --> 00:51:37.030
becoming more aware of the body
and the physical sensation.

00:51:37.030 --> 00:51:39.910
Still maintaining that
sense of lightness,

00:51:39.910 --> 00:51:41.540
that sense of
clarity, but becoming

00:51:41.540 --> 00:51:44.340
more aware of the weight
of the body again.

00:51:51.130 --> 00:51:52.970
More aware of the
feet on the floor.

00:51:58.980 --> 00:51:59.960
Hands on the legs.

00:52:05.630 --> 00:52:06.610
Noticing any sounds.

00:52:18.760 --> 00:52:23.630
And in your own time, when
you're ready, and just

00:52:23.630 --> 00:52:25.790
gently open the eyes again.

00:52:40.230 --> 00:52:42.600
OK.

