to scratch an itch.

00:56:59.430 --> 00:57:02.830
It feels weird to disobey
when you're bored.

00:57:02.830 --> 00:57:04.620
So I think it's a
great area to get

00:57:04.620 --> 00:57:06.300
curious about, because
if you can have

00:57:06.300 --> 00:57:10.742
some mastery over that
compulsion to occupy boredom,

00:57:10.742 --> 00:57:12.450
it unlocks a whole
bunch of other things.

00:57:12.450 --> 00:57:14.640
So we can either be
like, oh-- And as

00:57:14.640 --> 00:57:16.840
usual there's a balance
to be had, right?

00:57:16.840 --> 00:57:19.260
