01:00:27.980 --> 01:00:31.780
Labeling, sometimes even
labeling out loud for me,

01:00:31.780 --> 01:00:34.080
is really useful
during a time of storm.

01:00:34.080 --> 01:00:36.220
So it's not something
you graduate from,

01:00:36.220 --> 01:00:38.280
it's just that you
add other options.

01:00:38.280 --> 01:00:40.070
And silence becomes
one of those options.

01:00:40.070 --> 01:00:43.080
There's not a damn thing wrong
with counting, or labeling,

01:00:43.080 --> 01:00:45.760
or listening to a guided
meditation, either.

01:00:45.760 --> 01:00:49.730
ANDY PUDDICOMBE: Yeah, and
